structure.unit: FEES AND COMPENSATION OF PUBLIC OFFICERS AND EMPLOYEES

law.text: The commission shall file its reports with the Legislative Research Commission seventy-five (75) days prior to each session of the General Assembly. The Legislative Research Commission shall be responsible for the printing and distribution of the commission's reports to the members of the General Assembly.
law.history: Created 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 83, sec. 5, effective March 29, 1976.
